00:02:30.453 --> 00:02:34.373
Then we have past of this lifetime,

00:02:35.053 --> 00:02:38.773
and also we have past of our previous lives.

00:02:39.333 --> 00:02:42.493
Then all the past is built in within us

00:02:42.613 --> 00:02:44.893
since our creation.

