00:04:41.933 --> 00:04:47.093
is only cured if you know what's the problem of the left side is.

00:04:49.693 --> 00:04:54.213
So Mahavira went quite deep on to the left side.

00:04:54.733 --> 00:04:58.333
Why I said it's difficult the left side is, because

00:04:58.453 --> 00:05:01.253
when you start moving on the left side

00:05:01.413 --> 00:05:04.893
the movement becomes linear of course,

00:05:05.013 --> 00:05:07.813
but it moves downward,

00:05:08.373 --> 00:05:12.533
while the movement on the right side moves upward.

00:05:12.693 --> 00:05:17.133
So the movement goes down like that,

00:05:18.013 --> 00:05:22.973
and then it coils up,

00:05:23.853 --> 00:05:26.653
forms coils,

00:05:26.813 --> 00:05:28.853
and you go on moving with it

00:05:29.333 --> 00:05:32.413
so you are lost in the coil.

00:05:32.853 --> 00:05:36.293
