00:05:36.413 --> 00:05:38.973
and the coils are not so many,

00:05:39.133 --> 00:05:43.173
and because it is upward it's easy to get out of it.

00:05:45.613 --> 00:05:48.533
So those people who go to the left,

00:05:48.653 --> 00:05:52.573
by any chance, by thinking too much about their past,

00:05:52.693 --> 00:05:56.933
crying about themselves and always complaining,

00:05:57.693 --> 00:06:01.773
are more difficult than the people on the right side.

00:06:02.773 --> 00:06:05.693
But the right side people are troublesome to others,

00:06:05.813 --> 00:06:09.333
while the left side people are troublesome to themselves.

00:06:09.813 --> 00:06:12.253
That's how this left side

00:06:12.373 --> 00:06:16.413
was to be found out properly, was done by Mahavira.

00:06:16.973 --> 00:06:19.973
Of course He knew also, I think, all about it.

00:06:20.293 --> 00:06:26.013
So He has mentioned practically,

00:06:26.173 --> 00:06:29.773
in details, lots of things that can happen to a person

