Now we may say that Mahavira is sometimes seen

00:23:46.613 --> 00:23:49.493
as a person who is naked.

00:23:49.613 --> 00:23:53.493
So it happened that He had gone in a jungle to meditate

00:23:53.613 --> 00:23:56.613
and to find out about the left side

00:23:56.733 --> 00:23:58.893
and when He got up, you see,

00:23:59.013 --> 00:24:03.373
He got caught up in one of the bushes

00:24:03.533 --> 00:24:11.453
and He had to torn off half part of that.

00:24:11.693 --> 00:24:16.213
When that half part was torn off,

00:24:16.333 --> 00:24:21.493
then He came out of those bushes and He was all right,

00:24:21.613 --> 00:24:25.173
but at the same time Shri Krishna appeared there on the scene

00:24:25.293 --> 00:24:27.853
as a little boy from a village

00:24:27.973 --> 00:24:30.973
and He said that "I'm a poor man,"

00:24:31.093 --> 00:24:34.373
this little boy said, "I am a poor person, I have nothing with Me.

00:24:34.493 --> 00:24:37.293
You are a king. You can always get your clothes.

00:24:37.413 --> 00:24:43.733
Why don't you give Me Your, this half cloth that You have?"

00:24:43.853 --> 00:24:50.653
And, they say so that it was given to this boy

00:24:50.773 --> 00:24:52.053
and who ran away.

00:24:52.173 --> 00:24:54.853
He was nobody else but Shri Vishnu.

00:24:56.653 --> 00:25:02.173
And this, you see, Vishnu took away that cloth

00:25:02.293 --> 00:25:05.773
and of hardly for about two seconds or three seconds

00:25:05.893 --> 00:25:07.733
because He was a king you see,

00:25:07.853 --> 00:25:09.653
and He hid Himself with leaves

00:25:09.773 --> 00:25:12.973
and He went to His palace and got dressed.

00:25:13.093 --> 00:25:15.693
But imagine, the people, how negative they are.

00:25:15.813 --> 00:25:19.693
They just walk without clothes - Jainies.

00:25:19.933 --> 00:25:24.093
They have, you see, all kinds of taboos

00:25:24.213 --> 00:25:27.813
against all the worms, everything.

00:25:28.173 --> 00:25:30.893
It's said, these people have started,

00:25:31.013 --> 00:25:33.973
that if you do not respect these little, little animals,

00:25:34.093 --> 00:25:39.693
like you can a, even serpent

00:25:39.813 --> 00:25:45.173
or any animal which is troublesome and bad,

00:25:45.293 --> 00:25:52.253
but is a living thing, so it's to be preserved.

00:25:52.453 --> 00:25:54.173
Now these Jains are mad.

00:25:54.293 --> 00:25:58.013
I told you that they have gone to such a limit of vegetarianism

00:25:58.133 --> 00:26:00.413
that they try to save even the bugs,

00:26:00.533 --> 00:26:02.693
put the bugs in a hut,

00:26:02.813 --> 00:26:07.133
and the hut has got a brahmin there.

00:26:07.253 --> 00:26:11.413
Now these bugs suck the blood of this brahmin

00:26:11.533 --> 00:26:15.173
and once the brahmin is

00:26:15.293 --> 00:26:17.533
completely, I mean I should say, sucked in

00:26:17.653 --> 00:26:20.613
by these bugs, they fall on the ground.

00:26:20.733 --> 00:26:23.453
Then they allow the brahmin to come out

00:26:23.573 --> 00:26:25.773
and they give him a lot of dakshina, means

00:26:25.893 --> 00:26:28.013
they give him money as a reward

00:26:28.133 --> 00:26:31.933
for helping the bugs to suck his blood.

00:26:32.053 --> 00:26:34.253
This kind of vegetarianism is there.

00:26:34.373 --> 00:26:37.973
Beware of vegetarians. You see even Hitler was a vegetarian

00:26:38.093 --> 00:26:41.013
so you can imagine what sort of a vegetarianism it is.

00:26:41.133 --> 00:26:44.013
All these fads of vegetarianism and all that

00:26:44.133 --> 00:26:46.253
are not at all required,

00:26:46.413 --> 00:26:51.293
and that's what Mahavira showed in His life,

00:26:51.413 --> 00:26:56.333
that it is not at all important to bother about food,

00:26:56.453 --> 00:26:59.333
what they should eat.

00:26:59.453 --> 00:27:04.173
See, the whole theory of this vegetarianism has gone

00:27:04.293 --> 00:27:09.693
to such a nonsensical limits that I have told people

00:27:09.813 --> 00:27:13.493
that we should give up vegetarianism, completely.

00:27:13.613 --> 00:27:18.613
Now also see the juxtaposition of what He wanted to do.

00:27:18.853 --> 00:27:23.173
If you do not eat proteins you cannot fight bhoots.

00:27:23.293 --> 00:27:26.373
A person who has bhoots in him must eat a lot of proteins,

00:27:26.493 --> 00:27:29.413
not carbohydrates but proteins, so that

00:27:29.533 --> 00:27:33.613
it can fight those left-sided enemies.

00:27:33.733 --> 00:27:36.933
But here it is they have to be vegetarians.

00:27:37.053 --> 00:27:40.373
Now imagine they have left-sided enemies within them

00:27:40.493 --> 00:27:42.213
and they want to be vegetarians.

00:27:42.333 --> 00:27:45.693
Finished. How will they fight it?

00:27:45.813 --> 00:27:49.253
So all this is all we should say is pre-planned

00:27:49.373 --> 00:27:54.173
by the person who tries to, sort of say is -

00:27:54.293 --> 00:27:57.253
we can say like that, you see, a person

00:27:57.373 --> 00:28:01.733
who tries to remove the -

00:28:04.493 --> 00:28:10.373
or we can say that the person who tries to make the,

00:28:10.493 --> 00:28:14.013
these lower animals live,

00:28:14.133 --> 00:28:16.773
rather than human beings, you see they're oppressors.

00:28:16.893 --> 00:28:18.693
This is the stupid thing they do.

00:28:18.813 --> 00:28:23.573
Must know that I cannot give Realization to these worms

00:28:23.693 --> 00:28:29.653
and to these fishes, or even to chickens.

00:28:30.053 --> 00:28:32.933
We require human beings.

00:28:33.253 --> 00:28:40.893
So all this has happened because of human beings

00:28:41.013 --> 00:28:44.933
going in juxtaposition of whatever is said.

00:28:45.053 --> 00:28:49.573
Like Christ has said, "Thou shalt not have adulterous eyes,"

00:28:49.733 --> 00:28:52.893
and I've yet to come across a Christian

00:28:53.013 --> 00:28:56.453
who is not a Sahaja Yogi, without adulterous eyes,

00:28:56.573 --> 00:28:59.493
whether it's a woman or a man.

00:29:00.813 --> 00:29:05.253
So we go just the opposite of what we have been taught.

00:29:05.373 --> 00:29:09.493
In the case of same thing happened that Mahavira,

00:29:09.613 --> 00:29:13.813
what He tried to do was absolutely killed

00:29:13.933 --> 00:29:17.773
by these people who are trying

00:29:17.893 --> 00:29:22.773
to make this vegetarianism as a big religion.

00:29:23.453 --> 00:29:27.533
Also another thing was that this vegetarianism

00:29:27.653 --> 00:29:32.053
came into Jainism through one fellow called Neminath

00:29:32.173 --> 00:29:37.613
who was a tirthankar at the time of Shri Krishna.

00:29:37.773 --> 00:29:40.453
He was to be married. In those days they were married,

00:29:40.573 --> 00:29:43.773
not only but they were eating all kinds of meats

00:29:43.893 --> 00:29:48.733
and so many lambs and goats came for the wedding of this man

00:29:48.853 --> 00:29:52.933
so he felt that - uparati we call it, this:

00:29:53.053 --> 00:29:56.573
he didn't like it, he was disgusted, he was frustrated with that.

00:29:56.693 --> 00:30:00.173
With that frustration what did he do?

00:30:00.333 --> 00:30:02.973
He said, "I will not eat meat."

00:30:03.093 --> 00:30:07.173
And that's how vegetarianism started among Jainies.

00:30:07.293 --> 00:30:09.613
And that's how it's still going on,

00:30:09.733 --> 00:30:14.733
and these Jainies I find are the
joyless people, absolutely joyless.

00:30:14.853 --> 00:30:18.533
They're so much fond of money, they run after the money

00:30:18.653 --> 00:30:22.093
and they go on behaving in such a peculiar way

00:30:22.213 --> 00:30:24.253
that you can't understand, I mean they are

00:30:24.373 --> 00:30:26.853
human beings but the way they behave you can't

00:30:26.973 --> 00:30:29.533
understand them, they're not normal people.

00:30:30.853 --> 00:30:35.253
So we realize that despite all that Mahavira worked out,

00:30:35.373 --> 00:30:42.893
still the people are supposed to be His disciples,

00:30:43.053 --> 00:30:46.053
they are Jains, and they are like this.

00:30:46.653 --> 00:30:49.653
So what we have to do now is to understand

00:30:49.773 --> 00:30:53.293
that in Sahaja Yoga we'd better not do something of that kind.

00:30:53.893 --> 00:30:57.738
Whatever you are told, you have to understand why it is so,

00:30:57.859 --> 00:30:59.468
you know the modus operandi,

00:30:59.589 --> 00:31:01.773
you know each and everything about Sahaja Yoga.

00:31:01.893 --> 00:31:03.573
You know the whole subject

00:31:03.693 --> 00:31:07.333
so it's not proper for you to in any way,

00:31:07.453 --> 00:31:09.853
to succumb to any such arguments

00:31:09.973 --> 00:31:12.733
or any such big, big talks or big, big

00:31:12.853 --> 00:31:17.173
advertisement and take to something that is wrong.

00:31:17.333 --> 00:31:19.413
It's very important.

00:31:20.493 --> 00:31:24.293
We are Sahaja Yogis and we understand the balance.

00:31:24.453 --> 00:31:27.933
Of course I always say that Westerners for example,

00:31:28.093 --> 00:31:29.773
maybe Australians also,

00:31:29.893 --> 00:31:33.653
should take more to carbohydrates because they eat a lot of meat.

00:31:33.773 --> 00:31:35.693
So they can take to carbohydrates,

00:31:35.813 --> 00:31:38.373
but that doesn't mean vegetarianism by any chance.

00:31:38.493 --> 00:31:40.413
I mean, to compensate.

00:31:40.533 --> 00:31:44.133
And in India I always say they must take to more meats,

00:31:44.253 --> 00:31:46.053
as will do, do them good.

00:31:46.173 --> 00:31:50.733
But then by no means I say that you just eat meat and nothing else.

00:31:50.893 --> 00:31:53.213
But a balance has to be found out,

00:31:53.333 --> 00:31:55.013
and once you strike it

00:31:55.133 --> 00:32:00.053
then you'll be surprised that you'll feel so relaxed, so much better,

00:32:00.173 --> 00:32:02.493
so much enlightened

00:32:02.613 --> 00:32:06.253
and the vibrations will flow much better than normally.

00:32:06.413 --> 00:32:08.893
So for food, you have to be careful.

00:32:09.013 --> 00:32:10.813
Same about with clothes

00:32:10.933 --> 00:32:14.493
that you shouldn't go mad after a suit all the time

00:32:14.613 --> 00:32:17.853
whether it's hot or cold or indifferent.

00:32:17.973 --> 00:32:21.533
What you have to do is to wear something that will suit you.

00:32:21.653 --> 00:32:23.693
Now for example, in a climate like this

00:32:23.813 --> 00:32:27.413
you may require a suit or something to cover yourself,

00:32:27.533 --> 00:32:29.893
but supposing you are in Ganapatipule

00:32:30.013 --> 00:32:33.573
or some place like that where it's not so cold

00:32:33.693 --> 00:32:36.453
or so hot, maybe it's dry.

00:32:36.573 --> 00:32:39.813
So what sort of a dress you should wear which is comfortable,

00:32:39.933 --> 00:32:42.893
that should be found out. And whatever you find out

00:32:43.013 --> 00:32:45.293
that this is such a comfortable dress for us,

00:32:45.413 --> 00:32:47.213
you'd better do it.

00:32:47.333 --> 00:32:52.813
Because what I have seen in many - you see, it's a thing that

00:32:52.933 --> 00:32:54.853
whenever I tell you something,

00:32:54.973 --> 00:32:57.133
don't take it to the extremes

00:32:57.253 --> 00:32:59.053
and don't take a little bit of it.

00:32:59.173 --> 00:33:02.653
But when I tell you this thing, you must understand

00:33:02.813 --> 00:33:05.933
that whatever is good for you,

00:33:06.053 --> 00:33:10.773
whatever is your temperament, whatever is aptitude,

00:33:10.893 --> 00:33:14.413
you have to take something that will nourish that,

00:33:14.533 --> 00:33:17.533
that will improve you and give you a balance.

00:33:17.653 --> 00:33:20.973
So to balance yourself, if you think of Mahavira

00:33:21.093 --> 00:33:24.733
you must think also of Shri Hanumana,

00:33:24.853 --> 00:33:27.813
both these things are important.

